  "html": "<p>Hey ReFi Nation!</p><p>We are really excited to share that the <a href=\"https://refigratitude.xyz/\">ReFi Gratitude Collection</a> is now live! This project is a gift to enable this communitiy to express gratitude in a new way. Mint one for yourself, and get a twin mint to share with a friend as a token of gratitude!</p><p>These mints will demonstrate on-chain relationships between various actors in the ReFi movement in a unique way. </p><ul><li>50% of proceeds go towards <a href=\"https://twitter.com/BlackArtistFND\">The Black Artist Foundation</a> ‚Äî supporting a more just world of representation</li><li>50% of proceeds go towards retiring $NCT ‚Äî supporting nature-based regeneration<br></li></ul><div class=\"kg-card kg-button-card kg-align-center\"><a href=\"https://refi-gratitude.web.app/\" class=\"kg-btn kg-btn-accent\">Mint now</a></div><h2 id=\"gallery\">Gallery</h2><figure class=\"kg-card kg-gallery-card kg-width-wide kg-card-hascaption\"><div class=\"kg-gallery-container\"><div class=\"kg-gallery-row\"><div class=\"kg-gallery-image\"><img src=\"__GHOST_URL__/content/images/2022/12/image-30.png\" width=\"976\" height=\"984\" loading=\"lazy\" alt srcset=\"__GHOST_URL__/content/images/size/w600/2022/12/image-30.png 600w, __GHOST_URL__/content/images/2022/12/image-30.png 976w\" sizes=\"(min-width: 720px) 720px\"></div><div class=\"kg-gallery-image\"><img src=\"__GHOST_URL__/content/images/2022/12/image-31.png\" width=\"980\" height=\"964\" loading=\"lazy\" alt srcset=\"__GHOST_URL__/content/images/size/w600/2022/12/image-31.png 600w, __GHOST_URL__/content/images/2022/12/image-31.png 980w\" sizes=\"(min-width: 720px) 720px\"></div><div class=\"kg-gallery-image\"><img src=\"__GHOST_URL__/content/images/2022/12/image-32.png\" width=\"970\" height=\"980\" loading=\"lazy\" alt srcset=\"__GHOST_URL__/content/images/size/w600/2022/12/image-32.png 600w, __GHOST_URL__/content/images/2022/12/image-32.png 970w\" sizes=\"(min-width: 720px) 720px\"></div></div><div class=\"kg-gallery-row\"><div class=\"kg-gallery-image\"><img src=\"__GHOST_URL__/content/images/2022/12/image-33.png\" width=\"970\" height=\"972\" loading=\"lazy\" alt srcset=\"__GHOST_URL__/content/images/size/w600/2022/12/image-33.png 600w, __GHOST_URL__/content/images/2022/12/image-33.png 970w\" sizes=\"(min-width: 720px) 720px\"></div><div class=\"kg-gallery-image\"><img src=\"__GHOST_URL__/content/images/2022/12/image-34.png\" width=\"968\" height=\"978\" loading=\"lazy\" alt srcset=\"__GHOST_URL__/content/images/size/w600/2022/12/image-34.png 600w, __GHOST_URL__/content/images/2022/12/image-34.png 968w\" sizes=\"(min-width: 720px) 720px\"></div></div></div><figcaption>Mint a token of gratitude for you and a friend at https://refi-gratitude.web.app/</figcaption></figure><h2 id=\"how-it-works\">How it works</h2><p>1. Mint your NFTs now at <a href=\"https://refi-gratitude.web.app/\">ReFi-gratitude.web.app</a></p><p>2. Share your gratitude tweet(s) tagging others in the #ReFi space, and let them know you‚Äôd like to gift them your NFT twin</p><p>3. U<strong>se hashtag #ReFiGratitude in your tweet</strong></p><p>4. DM the person and get their wallet address so you can send them your NFT Twin using the <a href=\"https://refi-gratitude.web.app/\">ReFi-gratitude.web.app</a> dashboard</p><p>5. Join one of our daily Twitter Spaces between December 19th - December 23rd and publicly share your expressions of gratitude.<br></p><p>The spaces will be hosted on twitter in the following order from different friends in the ReFi space.</p><h2 id=\"daily-gratitude-spaces9am-pt-dec-19-23\">Daily Gratitude Spaces - 9am PT, Dec 19-23</h2><p>At 9am PT from Dec 19 to 23, we'll host a daily twitter spaces with friends from the ReFi space to reflect upon the year, express gratitude and mint NFTs! Check out the line-up</p><h3 id=\"day-1dec-19th-9am-ptrefidaoist-with-climatexcrypto\">Day 1 - Dec 19th 9am PT - <a href=\"https://twitter.com/i/spaces/1vOxwMBZzlPGB\">@ReFiDAOist with @climateXcrypto</a></h3><figure class=\"kg-card kg-embed-card\"><blockquote class=\"twitter-tweet\"><p lang=\"en\" dir=\"ltr\">Super excited to host the first daily <a href=\"https://twitter.com/hashtag/ReFiGratitude?src=hash&amp;ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">#ReFiGratitude</a> Twitter spaces tomorrow Dec 19 at 9am PT üéôÔ∏è<br><br>Here to express gratitude and reflect upon the last year in <a href=\"https://twitter.com/hashtag/ReFi?src=hash&amp;ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">#ReFi</a>! üôè<br><br>Hosted by <a href=\"https://twitter.com/climateXcrypto?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">@climateXcrypto</a> and frens! <br><br>Come join us üëè<a href=\"https://t.co/YFzP3VbjdZ\">https://t.co/YFzP3VbjdZ</a></p>&mdash; ReFi DAO (@ReFiDAOist) <a href=\"https://twitter.com/ReFiDAOist/status/1604396397599625218?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">December 18, 2022</a></blockquote>\n<script async src=\"https://platform.twitter.com/widgets.js\" charset=\"utf-8\"></script>\n</figure><h3 id=\"day-2dec-20threfipodcast-with-simarsmangat\">Day 2 - Dec 20th - <a href=\"https://twitter.com/i/spaces/1lPKqBldPDZGb\">@ReFiPodcast with @simarsmangat</a></h3><figure class=\"kg-card kg-embed-card\"><blockquote class=\"twitter-tweet\"><p lang=\"en\" dir=\"ltr\">We are grateful to have <a href=\"https://twitter.com/simarsmangat?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">@simarsmangat</a> host day 2 of the <a href=\"https://twitter.com/hashtag/ReFiGratitude?src=hash&amp;ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">#ReFiGratitude</a> collection‚Äôs Year In Review! <br><br>Come hang with frens, express gratitude and reflect upon the last year in climate and web3. <a href=\"https://t.co/iKWCswOPUB\">https://t.co/iKWCswOPUB</a></p>&mdash; ReFi Podcast (@ReFiPodcast) <a href=\"https://twitter.com/ReFiPodcast/status/1604397345671716865?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">December 18, 2022</a></blockquote>\n<script async src=\"https://platform.twitter.com/widgets.js\" charset=\"utf-8\"></script>\n</figure><h3 id=\"dec-21stloalabs-with-davefortson-and-btraux\">Dec 21st - @LOA_Labs with @dave_fortson and @btraux</h3><p>Spaces will be posted soon‚Äîfollow their account to get notified!</p><div class=\"kg-card kg-button-card kg-align-center\"><a href=\"https://twitter.com/loa_labs\" class=\"kg-btn kg-btn-accent\">Follow LOA Labs</a></div><h3 id=\"dec-22ndregennetwork\">Dec 22nd - @Regen_Network</h3><p>Spaces will be posted soon‚Äîfollow their account to get notified!</p><div class=\"kg-card kg-button-card kg-align-center\"><a href=\"https://twitter.com/regen_network\" class=\"kg-btn kg-btn-accent\">Follow Regen Network</a></div><h3 id=\"dec-23rdbasindao-with-tmo\">Dec 23rd - <a href=\"https://twitter.com/i/spaces/1OyKAVkLEQbGb\">@Basin.DAO with TMO</a></h3><figure class=\"kg-card kg-embed-card\"><blockquote class=\"twitter-tweet\"><p lang=\"en\" dir=\"ltr\">mark your calendars 12.23.22 <a href=\"https://twitter.com/hashtag/ReFiFriday?src=hash&amp;ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">#ReFiFriday</a> Reflection <br><br>with <a href=\"https://twitter.com/climateXcrypto?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">@climateXcrypto</a> <a href=\"https://twitter.com/antonio_paglino?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">@antonio_paglino</a> <a href=\"https://t.co/LA6HANIMGc\">https://t.co/LA6HANIMGc</a> <a href=\"https://t.co/BgCDBkwmln\">https://t.co/BgCDBkwmln</a></p>&mdash; tmo.basin of roaringfork.basin (@tmoindustries) <a href=\"https://twitter.com/tmoindustries/status/1601589186217541632?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">December 10, 2022</a></blockquote>\n<script async src=\"https://platform.twitter.com/widgets.js\" charset=\"utf-8\"></script>\n</figure><hr><h2 id=\"many-thanks\">Many thanks!</h2><p>‚Äî¬†<a href=\"https://twitter.com/ReFiDAOist\">ReFiDAO</a>, <a href=\"https://twitter.com/loa_labs\">LOA Labs</a>, <a href=\"https://twitter.com/realsimplelabs\">Real Simple Labs</a>, <a href=\"https://twitter.com/ReFiPodcast\">ReFiPodcast</a>, and <a href=\"https://twitter.com/BlackArtistFND\">Black Artists' Foundation</a></p>",
